properties.name: 45 Minutes
properties.description:
Imagine that it is about 45 minutes until the start of your weekly Wednesday night bike ride (you may not have to imagine very hard, here). That is not a very long time, we know. But imagine that in those next 45 minutes, you could be setting three world records in track and field and tying a fourth. Now that's something! Of course, we are not going to set any world records tonight, obviously, but we me just get close to greatness...
